Class ff_3DSModel.Face3DS

  • java.lang.Object
    • reuze.ff_3DSModel.Face3DS
  • Enclosing class:
    ff_3DSModel

    public class ff_3DSModel.Face3DS
extends java.lang.Object
    This is our face structure. This is is used for indexing into the vertex and texture coordinate arrays. From this information we know which vertices from our vertex array go to which face, along with the correct texture coordinates.
